title: Elite Jack!!
synopsis: The August issue of Shogakukan's Ciao magazine is announcing on Thursday that Meme Iwaoka's manga Elite Jack!! will get an anime adaptation. The anime will be on the Ciao Ciao TV bonus DVD that will be bundled with the September issue of the magazine on August 2.
staff: [['Imaizumi, Yuuichi', ['Sound Director']], ['Furuya, Yuuji', ['Sound Effects']], ['Meme, Iwaoka', ['Original Creator']], ['Shimizu, Keiichirou', ['Art Director']]]
